room_title: Escape room "Cartel Hostage Escape" by Escape Challenge in Rochester (MN)
room_description:
You are a Special Task Force unit tracking a cartel across the border. Part of your team has now been captured and are being held captive at a cartel safe house.
The rescue team has found the location where their team members are being held.  They can get into the safe house during the guard change.  They will need to find a way to get the prisoners out of their handcuffs, and the entire team will work together to find a new way out of the room.
You can choose to have the hostages handcuffed (Difficult) or Not Handcuffed (Moderate).
